g.text: Aim by cursor keys or tilt mobile device, fire by Space or Tap screen

text.tspan: You're submarine captain. Your submarine is trapped near water surface
because of sandbank. You could your U-Boat only rotate, but not move
and float away. if enemy will fire on you, they surely cannot miss you,
so send them sinking before they manage to fire! To kill enemy ship you
have to aim to the ship hull and not higher!!
You have only one torpedo chamber,
so you could fire not several torpedos simultaneously! Watch for enemy alert
informing you on which side new enemy appeared and control number of
already sinked - already generated - total in level ships on dashboard panels.
Ship icons will help you, red ones are sinked already, green ones remaining.
Do not kill innocent castaway on raft (has golden icon)! He is not going
to harm you. By killing him you loose some points, by letting him live - gain.
He will disapper after a while, just let him be...
Use cursor keys or tilt mobile device to control rotation of submarine.
Hold SHIFT key for more precise aiming. By SPACE key or TAPPING
screen you could fire and by ESC key abort game anytime...
